### Get all trips
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trip
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new trip
POST http://localhost:3000/api/trip
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_time": "2025-08-01T09:00:00Z",
  "end_time": "2025-08-01T13:00:00Z",
  "bus_id": 1,
  "src_station_id": 1,
  "dest_station_id": 2,
  "driver_id": 3
}

###

### Get a specific trip by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trip/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Update a trip by ID
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/trip/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "end_time": "2025-08-01T14:00:00Z",
  "driver_id": 5
}

###

### Delete a trip by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/trip/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get trips for a specific day (query param: date)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trip/day?date=2025-08-01
Accept: application/json

###

### Get trips for a specific month and year
GET http://localhost:3000/api/trip/month?month=8&year=2025
Accept: application/json
